categories: Category:Imperial Army officers of the Galactic Empire

nodes.text: Second Lieutenant Momo was an officer of the Imperial Army assigned to Jerec's battle group during the Galactic Civil War.

In 5 ABY, he wanted his companions to call him "Mad Dog Momo," but they refused, possibly due to his nice personality, young-looking face, or the fact that he had never fired a single shot. He served as an AT-ST driver for Yun on Ruusan.
